{"type":"message","id":"7f89d55d","parentId":"f8de15b1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:30:00.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The message tool needs a target. Since this is a cron job running in the main session and the user wants updates sent to Feishu, I need to figure out the target channel. Let me check if there's any configuration or context about where to send Feishu messages. Since I don't have that info, I should note that the message needs to be sent but I need the target channel ID.\n\nActually, looking at the task again, it says \"发送到飞书，让主人了解进展\" but doesn't specify which channel. In a cron context, I should probably ask or use a default. Let me check if there's any memory about Feishu channel configuration.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a210b55dd5f240918a1c4f26","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"feishu channel id 飞书 频道 配置","maxResults":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774330191175}}
