{"type":"message","id":"2ea660fb","parentId":"9f5d8857","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:30:06.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No Feishu channel configuration found in memory. Since this is a cron job and the task requires sending to Feishu, but I don't have the target channel ID, I should note this in my response. The file has been successfully updated, and I can report that the Feishu message requires a target channel configuration.\n\nLet me provide a summary to the user about what was completed.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **第 61 次牙齿再生深度思考完成！**\n\n**已保存：** `memory/牙齿再生研究日志.md`\n\n**本次主题：** 临床应用——从实验室到临床的转化路径\n\n**核心发现：**\n- 🎯 **监管路径是关键** - USAG-1 抗体药物（非细胞）将比组织工程牙胚早 5-8 年上市\n- 👶 **儿童市场是突破口** - 成本效益分析显示儿童患者 ICER 低于医保阈值，成人需等成本下降\n- 🇯🇵 **日本领跑全球** - Toregem Biopharma 已获 PMDA 批准，2024 Q4 完成首例患者入组\n\n**时间线预测：**\n| 里程碑 | 时间 |\n|--------|------|\n| 首个产品获批（日本） | 2034-2036 年 |\n| 组织工程牙胚获批（儿童） | 2038-2042 年 |\n| 成人适应症扩展 | 2042-2048 年 |\n| 广泛应用 | 2048-2055 年 |\n\n**⚠️ 飞书消息未发送** - 需要配置目标频道 ID（channel_id）。请在 HEARTBEAT.md 或 TOOLS.md 中配置飞书频道信息，或告知我应发送到哪个频道。\n\n---\n*下次思考将聚焦\"干细胞再生\"方向，深入分析牙髓干细胞与间充质干细胞的牙胚诱导效率*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774330200361}}
